  "summary": "实际上枚举数位就能解决了，考虑 <code>x000...</code> 有多少个保留的数，原本的十进制实际上退化成了<strong>九进制</strong>。",
  "link": "https://codeforces.com/gym/105257/problem/G",
  "link_text": "Problem - G - Codeforces",
  "source": "",
  "aliases": [],
  "parent": null,
  "format": "logseq",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "题目描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "但某一天，他发现 \\(1,2,\\ldots,9\\) 这九个数字中的 \\(x\\) 消失了，也就是说所有包含 \\(x\\) 这个数字的数都消失了。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "现在，他希望你能帮助他求出这九个数中 \\(x\\) 在未消失的自然数中小到大排在第几位。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输入描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "本题有多组测试数据，输入第一行为一个整数 \\(T\\) (\\(1 \\leq T \\leq 10^5\\))，表示测试数据的组数。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于每组测试数据：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "共一行两个整数 \\(n, x\\) (\\(0 \\leq n \\leq 10^{18}, 1 \\leq x \\leq 9\\))，由空格隔开，含义如题目描述所述。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "数据保证 \\(n\\) 中不包含数字 \\(x\\)。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "输出描述",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "对于每组测试数据：输出一行一个整数，表示 \\(x\\) 在未消失的自然数中小到大的排名。",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "样例",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "输入",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "5\n9 4\n99 7\n12345678 9\n9475632111234123 8\n998244353114514 7",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "输出",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "code",
              "lang": "",
              "code": "9\n81\n6053445\n1758041005111510\n205404686678741",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "无",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "void solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tll n, x; cin >> n >> x;\n\tstring s = to_string(n);\n\tvar p = vector<ll>(s.size() + 1);\n\tp[0] = 1;\n\tfa(i, 1, vs(p))p[i] = p[i - 1] * 9;\n\tll ans = 0;\n\tfa(i, 0, vs(s)) {\n\t\tll now = s[i] - '0';\n\t\tif (now >= x)ans += p[(int)s.size() - i - 1] * (now - 1);\n\t\telse ans += p[(int)s.size() - i - 1] * now;\n\t}\n\tcout << ans + 1 << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
